stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> NoFile
    NoFile --> FileSelected : File dropped/selected
    FileSelected --> Validating : Check format
    Validating --> Invalid : Bad format
    Invalid --> NoFile
    Validating --> Uploading : Valid format
    Uploading --> Processing : Server parsing
    Processing --> Complete : Import done
    Processing --> PartialFail : Some records failed
    Complete --> [*]
    PartialFail --> [*]